    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for COU2 is accepted at Low assurance level consistent with the current state of evidence. Seven of thirteen credibility factors have been assessed; all show achieved levels below required levels for MRL 5. Six factors remain not-assessed, representing documented epistemic gaps. The decision to accept at Low assurance reflects the early-stage nature of the evidence package and does not constitute regulatory clearance. Validation results from five operating points are included; however, the generation activity provenance for operating points 2 and 4 was not captured in the structured evidence record — these results derive from legacy experimental campaigns where activity metadata was not systematically recorded. The team acknowledges this as an epistemic provenance gap and commits to remediation in the next evidence cycle.",
